    <data key="d0">Intellect Design Fabric Data Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AS2JeM2FUzE</data>
    <data key="d2">Big data platform processing 1-2M messages for risk profiling. Migrated from MongoDB on EC2 to MongoDB Atlas with VPC Peering.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive</data>
